# 📝 To-Do List Android App
A simple and efficient **To-Do List App** built as part of my Android development journey. This app helps users manage their daily tasks with a clean and intuitive interface.

## 🚀 Features
➕ Add new tasks
✏️ Update existing tasks
❌ Delete tasks
📋 Simple and user-friendly UI
💾 Local data storage

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
* Language: Kotlin
* IDE: Android Studio
* Architecture: MVVM
* Storage: RoomDB

## 📦 APK Download Guide
Follow these steps to download and install the APK:

1. Go to the Releases section of this repository
2. Click on the latest version
3. Download the `.apk` file
4. Open the downloaded file on your Android device
5. If prompted, enable "Install from unknown sources"
6. Install and launch the app 🎉

## 💻 Run Locally (For Developers)
1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/your-username/your-repo-name.git
   ```
2. Open the project in Android Studio
3. Sync Gradle
4. Run the app on an emulator or physical device

